iu.com/article/47YiTzaHEk3 }}</ref>

== 個人生活 ==
1995年5月16日，伊姆蘭在[[巴黎|巴黎]]和英國名媛[[珍美瑪·罕|珍美瑪·歌斯密]]結婚。兩人育有兩名兒子：蘇萊曼（Sulaiman）及卡西姆（Kasim）。因為珍美瑪有一半[[猶太人|猶太人]]血統，伊姆蘭婚後從政的決定引起政敵及情報局的懷疑並被伊斯蘭政黨利用指控他和[[錫安主義|猶太復國主義者]]有關係。伊姆蘭和珍美瑪在2004年6月22日宣布離婚<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/3829383.stm "Imran Khan and Jemima divorce"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/3829383.stm |date=20190126230209 }}. BBC News. 22 June, 2004.</ref>，主要原因是因珍美瑪在適應在巴基斯坦的生活上有困難<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2066533/Imran-Khan-reveals-torment-break-Jemima-Goldsmith-marriage.html "'I almost lost the will to live': Imran Khan reveals torment over break-up of his marriage to Jemima Goldsmith"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130505043811/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2066533/Imran-Khan-reveals-torment-break-Jemima-Goldsmith-marriage.html |date=2013-05-05 }}. DailyMail. 26 November, 2011.</ref>及伊姆蘭的政敵針對珍美瑪所造成的壓力。

2015年1月8日，在多日傳聞之下，伊姆蘭在其[[伊斯蘭堡|伊斯蘭堡]]的家中公布和英國籍巴基斯坦裔記者[[萊罕姆·罕|萊罕姆·罕]]結婚的消息。<ref>[http://www.dawn.com/news/1155695/imran-and-reham-khan-tie-the-knot-in-bani-gala "Imran and Reham Khan tie the knot in Bani Gala"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1155695/imran-and-reham-khan-tie-the-knot-in-bani-gala |date=20150108121954 }}. Dawn News. 8 January 2015.</ref>萊罕姆後來指出兩人早於2014年10月結婚，但當時未有即時公佈婚訊。萊罕姆之前曾經有過一段婚姻並和前夫育有三名孩子。

2015年10月30日，伊姆蘭和萊罕姆宣布因性格不合而結束他們只有十個月的婚姻。<ref>[http://www.dawn.com/news/1216546 "Imran, Reham part ways"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1216546 |date=20190515143152 }}. Dawn News. 31 October 2015.</ref>兩人離婚後關係惡劣。萊罕姆開始批評伊姆蘭及其政黨並在2018年7月出版的爭議性自傳中披露她和伊姆蘭的婚姻生活及他的政治活動。<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5995775/Imran-Khans-second-ex-wife-slates-stolen-mandate-warns-Pakistan-stuck-him.html “'Pakistan can't walk away from Imran like I did': Ex-wife number two slates cricket legend's 'stolen' victory and warns the country is 'now stuck with him'”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5995775/Imran-Khans-second-ex-wife-slates-stolen-mandate-warns-Pakistan-stuck-him.html |date=20190222153609 }}. Daily Mail. 26-07-2018.</ref>伊姆蘭·汗亦在訪問中指他和萊罕姆的婚姻是他「人生中最大的錯誤」。<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5978249/I-didnt-glimpse-mystic-brides-face-married-says-Imran-Khan.html “I didn't get a glimpse of my mystic bride's face until after we married, says Imran Khan as he calls his second marriage to TV weather girl 'the biggest mistake of my life'”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5978249/I-didnt-glimpse-mystic-brides-face-married-says-Imran-Khan.html |date=20210205184808 }}. Daily Mail. 22-07-2018.</ref>

自2016年開始，媒體開始報導伊姆蘭和他靈性導師[[布希拉·伊姆蘭|布希拉·瑪內卡]]（Bushra Maneka）結婚的傳聞。伊姆蘭及瑪內卡的家人均否認報導，但伊姆蘭政黨的祕書署在2018年1月7日承認伊姆蘭已經向瑪內卡求婚。同年2月18日，正義運動黨公佈伊姆蘭及瑪內卡已結婚的消息。<ref>[https://www.dawn.com/news/1390200 “PTI confirms Imran Khan's marriage to Bushra Maneka in Lahore”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1390200 |date=20181225223341 }}. Dawn News. 18-02-2018.</ref>

